<br>
It was funny how he tried to play on our sympathies, saying he was lost and brand new to the game, yet he knew how to wheel and deal in the bazaar?!?!<br>
<br>
The whole thing was REAL fishy.  We never figured out exactly what his scam was, or how it worked, but we knew it was a scam.  We discussed the situation among our officers and prompty booted him from the guild.<br>
<br>
I was so mad, I kinda wished it was a PvP server, so i could camp his spawn and gank him over and over...  (And believe me, I'm not a mean player.  That is just how MAD it makes me when people like this dupe REAL newbs and people who are too honest and innocent to smell a rat!)<br>
<br>
